  <brief_title>Clinical Outcomes of Tiotropium Plus Fluticasone Propionate/Salmeterol Compared With Tiotropium for Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) in Korea</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open Label, Multicenter, Phase 4 Study for the Comparison of Efficacy of Tiotropium Plus Salmeterol/ Fluticasone Propionate Compared With Tiotropium Alone in COPD Patients</official_title>
